<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title></title>
</head>

<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #333;">
    <p>Dear Colleague,</p>
    <p>  Kindly be informed that you have been assigned to the Customer Complaint ID: {!Case.CaseNumber} has been created by {!Case.CreatedBy} in the responsibility of the {!Case.Plant__c} team. </p>

    <p> <strong>Next Steps (Investigation Team): </strong><br> Support the complaint coordinator with investigating the complaint, identifying the root cause, and defining/executing the corrective action plan. </p>

  <h3>Ticket Details:</h3>
    <table cellpadding="5" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="border-collapse: collapse;">
        <tr>
            <td><strong>Customer:</strong></td>
            <td>{!Case.Account}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><strong>Subject:</strong></td>
            <td>{!Case.Subject}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><strong>Product:</strong></td>
            <td>{!Case.Product__c}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><strong>Detailed Description:</strong></td>
            <td>{!Case.Description}</td>
        </tr>
    </table>


    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p>Your CRM Support Team</p>
    <p> Link to Ticket in mySalesForce:<a href="{!Case.Link}" style="color: #1a73e8;">{!Case.Subject}</a> </p>
    <p> The mySalesForce system automatically generated this message. </p>
</body>

</html>